            Colocar ip fixo no linux: 

                                nano /etc/network/interfaces
                                Descar até o final e adicionar essa linha >


                                 auto <interface de rede> ex: auto ens33
                                iface <interface de rede> inet static
                                address [IP do debian]
                                 netmask [Mascara de subrede]
                                gateway [Gateway do debian]

                                reiniciar - systemctl restart networking


            Configurar pfsense para pingar o gateway:


                                Interface>Assignments
                                        Add

                                        enable
                                        IP static
                                        colocar o gateway
                                        /24
                                        save

